*Ovde* se nalazim u potpunosti srećan. (Here I am completely happy.)

*Ovde* je veoma važno da se pridržavamo pravila. (Here it is very important to follow the rules.)

Moj dom se nalazi *ovde*. (My home is located here.)

Malo smo se zadržali *ovde*, a onda smo nastavili put. (We stopped here for a while and then continued on our way.)

*Ovde* je vreme veoma nepredvidivo. (The weather is very unpredictable here.)